{"tid":272711,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲打有冇試過喺expedia訂錯酒店","createTime":"2017-06-06T04:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T16:24:21.000Z","uid":104313,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59cf1c097d73fd7b535f000c30b2d2de923c80a1","tid":272711,"uid":104313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"原本諗住開開心心去澳門旅行<br />\n點知....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始上expedia網諗住訂間平啲既酒店<br />\n我就用氹仔 澳門呢啲準確啲既字眼搵<br />\n希望咁樣可以搵間喺氹仔附近既酒店<br />\n一㩒入去就見到有間好平既酒店<br />\n咁我就㩒埋入去睇下環境設備啦<br />\n全部野都齊環境又好  咩都無問題<br />\n係離氹仔遠啲 有7點幾公里遠<br />\n以為好近<br />\n我就網上比錢訂呢間<br />\n訂完就搵搵確實地點<br />\n點知間酒店喺珠海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我打去服務熱線問<br />\n酒店就話不設退款 expedia開頭就話會比翻份report我睇<br />\n應該有得由expedia退款<br />\n成件事已經成半個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都未有咩咩report<br />\n今日打去問又比人話翻轉頭話我       自己無眼睇？<br />\n想問下其實係唔係真係退唔到錢<br />\n雖則得500幾蚊  但咁樣唔見幾百真係好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1393ab09463cde237d838141d5b44fc2824183fe","tid":272711,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"不設退款4隻字好難解咩<br />\n自己心急睇錯訂錯係你問題"},{"pid":"69935baff837a25055c1ed865e5c4939eaff35a1","tid":272711,"uid":48913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:42:38.000Z","msg":"弱智真係唔好去旅行<br />\n留番喺香港啦 唔好勉強"},{"pid":"ed708076876b485d158fd0bd84c15334fb3170b6","tid":272711,"uid":101367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"Expedia 有啲係可以唔知幾多日內退係全數退 但其實你唔應該問酒店 因為你經咗agent 所有條款睇agent<br />\n不過你check返你email 佢應該有講有無得退 無就你收皮"},{"pid":"4fc81f97e6e053ee6f5722bf92fe3252ac4469d3","tid":272711,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"自己錯仲想人退錢？<br />\n點都講唔通啦"},{"pid":"562d2cf92281b5cd0a2017620a84120b881f7e4e","tid":272711,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"訂酒店唔睇地圖先買，5舊水一個教訓抵到喊啦。"},{"pid":"d4df43323d3d02e94ae58cad90a2071558a6ae4c","tid":272711,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:14:09.000Z","msg":"咁都有得搞錯<br />\n祝你好運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36dd693f75ce9b5e18e1f46b5147050a687e3c62","tid":272711,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce794cc0e0bee6c4cffdf6a124273ca6c2df3315","tid":272711,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"應該可以同酒店個邊退 不過可能要比手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2563925861e25e1ccaeebc0fef5592e8c2348a4","tid":272711,"uid":44593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:44:44.000Z","msg":"驗IQ啦懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac223bc3bc00b2ee3b9f67de7aeed38cf1196e5","tid":272711,"uid":83853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"試過 去Sweden book 錯左第二個月份 <br />\n<br />\n去到間酒店 即幫我 退返入信用咭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45671e947f831fedadc1ff33e3e45697af842a88","tid":272711,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T06:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該可以同酒店個邊退 不過可能要比手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒店唔一定退啦，如果係BOOK 講明無得退果啲。<br />\n<br />\n改期就或者會同你做。<br />\n<br />\n如果BOOK果啲講明不設取消退款都可以有得退，咁仲邊有人用可以取消退款果啲BOOK。<br />\n<br />\n講明無得取消果啲，俾你退係人情，無得退係道理。"},{"pid":"7398081e5d9dda181beeb62b6c1cf2df3ce224cb","tid":272711,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"弱智真係唔好網上訂酒店啦<br />\n去旅行社比錢人搞啦"},{"pid":"7fe9c9311e1b88e13cf1cb4391e64d0176f93fab","tid":272711,"uid":37316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:20:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我就網上比錢訂呢間<br />\n訂完就搵搵確實地點</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d8beb50624bc3ca4e19bba856fc65d5ce73d9b","tid":272711,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該可以同酒店個邊退 不過可能要比手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒店唔一定退啦，如果係BOOK 講明無得退果啲。<br />\n<br />\n改期就或者會同你做。<br />\n<br />\n如果BOOK果啲講明不設取消退款都可以有得退，咁仲邊有人用可以取消退款果啲BOOK。<br />\n<br />\n講明無得取消果啲，俾你退係人情，無得退係道理。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講明不設退款係Expedia 唔退比你姐，酒店有機會退，不過唔好抱咁大希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5d7c84474f59142b6535ce610bba1bb2778068","tid":272711,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該可以同酒店個邊退 不過可能要比手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒店唔一定退啦，如果係BOOK 講明無得退果啲。<br />\n<br />\n改期就或者會同你做。<br />\n<br />\n如果BOOK果啲講明不設取消退款都可以有得退，咁仲邊有人用可以取消退款果啲BOOK。<br />\n<br />\n講明無得取消果啲，俾你退係人情，無得退係道理。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講明不設退款係Expedia 唔退比你姐，酒店有機會退，不過唔好抱咁大希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果係由 expedia 收，唔係酒店收呢？<br />\n<br />\n我試過酒店收，我直接 email 酒店，酒店佢都話冇得退，但準我改期。"},{"pid":"4a6cc558cba6b303ba1d795dccbeeed8464f3a20","tid":272711,"uid":114909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:24:21.000Z","msg":"除非你只係訂錯日期，唔係都好難會同你搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}